tener instalado cv2

pip install opencv-python
http://ironsistem.com/tutoriales/python/deteccion-facial-en-python-y-opencv/

tener instalado requests
pip install requests

en caso de error:
ERROR: Can not perform a '--user' install. User site-packages are not visible in this virtualenv.
para arreglar 
nano /etc/pip.config
cambiar a user = false